          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p>This privacy policy applies to the Site. This privacy policy does not necessarily apply to any offline collection of your personal information. Please see below for details.</p>
          <p> We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices on any web site not operated by Park Towers Supermarkets to which the Site links or that links to the Site.</p>
